text: Helen Boyle (born 1907, date of death unknown) was a British swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:Year of death missing Category:British female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Female backstroke swimmers
